			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hey guys, I was thinking about the fire pet and how to possibly make him a DPS pet, therefor raid worthy.
<br />

<br />
- 5000 point mana pool would work.
<br />
- Low level wizard nukes *low 40s or mid 30s. Maybe a RARE ice comet.
<br />
- Innate Flowing Thought 15
<br />
- Casts his own concussion or two after around 3 nukes. 
<br />

<br />
With such small nukes, the pet would rarely run out of mana, therefore stay away from the mob *like we want*. To keep him from running toward the mob the FT 15 would be a big help.
<br />

<br />
And remember those low level nukes can do damage if the pet keeps casting them.
<br />

<br />
Concussion from the pet would erase agro from the MASTER. This would help us with our agro problem.
<br />

<br />
This is just a suggestion, thoughts?<br />_________________<br />Master Sithro, 65 Arch Convoker - Bring it ye one-eyed bitch! - of Unbound Destiny</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
