				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I like the previous idea made by Xuthaz but I would make a few tweaks to the idea.
<br />

<br />
1)  Have fire pet cast fire or ice nukes.  If the idea is to have a pet that puts out steady dps, then the pet needs to be able to land nukes on all types of mob resists.  Also, you would have to program the pet so that if it does get a full resist, then it will change its nuke preference.
<br />

<br />
