<br />

<br />
Servant of Marr 2:
<br />

<br />
This would be  just like the AAXP point skill Servant of Ro. Single target pet, rooted in place, casting nukes (cold based as a Marr Pet) that does a 500 point DD spell every 2.5 seconds (2.5 second recast time), for 100 DPS. As you add focus items it goes higher. Make the pet cost 400 mana, and unlimited mana, it stays till the mob is dead. Sure I know it sounds like the Servant of Ro pet we get now, but lobs ice not fire. Works identical to servant of ro. So we know the coding is in place for it. I don't know about the rest of you, but this pet I would use a lot where a regualr pet is not allowed as in Plane of Water, Fennin Ro Fights, Sol Ro Fights, etc.. Very useful, coding now in place (just needs a few tweaks), and good to go. A fire and forget pet so to speak. Once made it is on auto attack, mobmoves out of range, well the pet stops and waits for it to get back in range, as it can't move. Of course we can /pet get lost  and get closer to remake it. The spells should be Dd, with a range of 200. The range increases as you add focus items to a max of 300, simular to a bolt. Line of sight has to be maintained though. 
<br />

<br />
Thoughts?
