that could work, but you'd probably also want a +mana only spell that's quick casting and low mana cost, with a decently high recast time.  maybe a cheap AA so it doesn't take up a spell gem.  if your pet isn't taking any damage, then you are wasting time/mana to increase your pet's nuke damage when you could be nuking yourself :p  Just thinking about raiding mages for a min, you already spend enough time/mana on the pet, you need a low maintenance pet.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=754455" target="_blank" class="postlink">Elder Xuthaz Everhate</a>
